lex items-center gap-2 group\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm group-hover:shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-purple-500/25 transition-shadow\">A</div><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white hidden sm:block\">AI 伴侣</span></a><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200 text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5\" href=\"/dashboard\">我的伴侣</a><a class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200 text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5\" href=\"/characters/create\">创建角色</a></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><a href=\"/login\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 font-medium transition-all duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500/50 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 text-white hover:from-purple-600 hover:to-pink-600 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-lg\">登录</button></a></div></div></div></nav><main class=\"pt-16 min-h-screen\"><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><section class=\"relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0\"><div class=\"absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-72 h-72 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-full blur-[128px]\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-pink-500/15 rounded-full blur-[128px]\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-purple-500/5 rounded-full blur-[100px]\"></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"flex justify-center gap-6 mb-8\"><span class=\"text-3xl animate-float\" style=\"animation-delay:0s\">💕</span><span class=\"text-3xl animate-float\" style=\"animation-delay:0.3s\">✨</span><span class=\"text-3xl animate-float\" style=\"animation-delay:0.6s\">🌟</span><span class=\"text-3xl animate-float\" style=\"animation-delay:0.8999999999999999s\">💬</span><span class=\"text-3xl animate-float\" style=\"animation-delay:1.2s\">🌙</span></div><h1 class=\"text-5xl sm:text-7xl font-bold mb-6\">你的<span class=\"text-gradient\"> AI 灵魂伴侣</span></h1><p class=\"text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-400 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">创建一个独一无二的 AI 虚拟伴侣，选择性格、设定背景，在每一次对话中建立情感连接。<br/>从陌生到熟悉，从朋友到知己，见证关系的每一步成长。</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4\"><a href=\"/register\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 font-medium transition-all duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500/50 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 text-white hover:from-purple-600 hover:to-pink-600 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg px-8 py-3.5 text-lg rounded-xl text-lg px-10\">开始体验</button></a><a href=\"/login\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 font-medium transition-all duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500/50 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed bg-white/10 text-white border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 px-8 py-3.5 text-lg rounded-xl text-lg px-8\">登录</button></a></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-16\">强大功能，<span class=\"text-gradient\">温暖陪伴</span></h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"glass rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">🎭</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3\">多样性格</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">从温柔到高冷，从开朗到神秘，8种性格任你选择，打造独一无二的 AI 伴侣。</p></div><div class=\"glass rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">💭</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3\">长期记忆</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">AI 会记住你们的点点滴滴，从喜好到经历，每一次对话都让关系更进一步。</p></div><div class=\"glass rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">💕</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3\">亲密度系统</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">从陌生人到灵魂伴侣，10个亲密度等级，见证关系的每一步成长。</p></div><div class=\"glass rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">🎨</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3\">角色自定义</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">自定义角色的名字、性格、背景故事、爱好，创造最符合你理想的伴侣。</p></div><div class=\"glass rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">🤖</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3\">AI 驱动</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">基于先进 AI 模型驱动的智能对话，自然流畅，让每次交流都充满温度。</p></div><div class=\"glass rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">🔒</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3\">隐私安全</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">你的数据安全有保障，私密对话只属于你。</p></div></div></div></section><footer class=\"border-t border-white/10 py-8 text-center text-sm text-gray-500\"><p>AI 伴侣 © <!-- -->2026<!-- --> — 用心创造，用 AI 陪伴</p></footer></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-87a4096ed2b4d747.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[7682,[\\\"730\\\",\\\"static/chunks/44530001-5b1be0b4145a7398.js\\\",\\\"613\\\",\\\"static/chunks/613-2e978c1d8071a92f.js\\\",\\\"112\\\",\\\"static/chunks/112-41eba7adb3078d46.js\\\",\\\"394\\\",\\\"static/chunks/394-292383b1eedfe6d0.js\\\",\\\"177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-4a1f4